{"notes":[{"type":2,"layer":0,"start":{"start":5,"width":5},"end":{"start":5,"width":5},"startTime":42,"endTime":46},{"type":1,"layer":0,"start":{"start":5,"width":10},"end":{"start":8,"width":5},"startTime":62,"endTime":66},{"type":1,"layer":0,"start":{"start":9,"width":3},"end":{"start":9,"width":3},"startTime":67,"endTime":68},{"type":1,"layer":0,"start":{"start":9,"width":3},"end":{"start":9,"width":3},"startTime":69,"endTime":69.5},{"type":1,"layer":0,"start":{"start":9,"width":3},"end":{"start":9,"width":3},"startTime":71,"endTime":71.5},{"type":0,"layer":0,"start":{"start":9,"width":3},"end":{"start":9,"width":3},"startTime":86.5,"endTime":87.5},{"type":0,"layer":0,"start":{"start":9,"width":3},"end":{"start":9,"width":3},"startTime":88.5,"endTime":89.5},{"type":0,"layer":0,"start":{"start":8,"width":3},"end":{"start":8,"width":3},"startTime":90.5,"endTime":91.5},{"type":0,"layer":0,"start":{"start":7,"width":3},"end":{"start":7,"width":3},"startTime":92.5,"endTime":93.5},{"type":1,"layer":0,"start":{"start":8,"width":2},"end":{"start":9,"width":2},"startTime":94.5,"endTime":97.5},{"type":2,"layer":0,"start":{"start":6,"width":1},"end":{"start":7,"width":1},"startTime":94.5,"endTime":97.5},{"type":2,"layer":0,"start":{"start":11,"width":1},"end":{"start":12,"width":1},"startTime":94.5,"endTime":97.5},{"type":0,"layer":0,"start":{"start":8,"width":4},"end":{"start":8,"width":4},"startTime":98.5,"endTime":99},{"type":1,"layer":0,"start":{"start":9,"width":3},"end":{"start":9,"width":3},"startTime":73,"endTime":73.5},{"type":1,"layer":0,"start":{"start":9,"width":3},"end":{"start":9,"width":3},"startTime":75,"endTime":75.5},{"type":1,"layer":0,"start":{"start":9,"width":3},"end":{"start":9,"width":3},"startTime":77,"endTime":77.5},{"type":1,"layer":0,"start":{"start":9,"width":3},"end":{"start":9,"width":3},"startTime":79,"endTime":79.5},{"type":1,"layer":0,"start":{"start":9,"width":3},"end":{"start":9,"width":3},"startTime":81,"endTime":81.5},{"type":1,"layer":0,"start":{"start":9,"width":3},"end":{"start":9,"width":3},"startTime":83,"endTime":83.5},{"type":1,"layer":0,"start":{"start":9,"width":3},"end":{"start":9,"width":3},"startTime":85,"endTime":85.5}],"events":[{"time":1.982479934036475,"duration":5.034980965923928,"type":"text","text":"Hello!"},{"time":7.993728910394407,"duration":5.015289590927501,"type":"text","text":"Welcome to [color=acred]Slide[/color][color=acblue]Tap[/color]!"},{"time":14.164593623711811,"duration":9.039024390243902,"type":"text","text":"SlideTap is a game played through [i]two[/i] basic\nmechanics: [b]sliding[/b] and [b]tapping[b]."},{"time":18.295759148326347,"duration":4.89390243902439,"type":"text","text":"Creative, I know."},{"time":24.157547766212527,"duration":3.3447154471544716,"type":"text","text":"Let's begin with [b]sliding[/b]."},{"time":27.96073119620967,"duration":5.815040650406504,"type":"text","text":"Your home row [color=#aaa][ASDFGHJKL;][/color] can\nbe used to move the [b]cursor[/b]."},{"time":34.05280436694137,"duration":8.95528455284553,"type":"text","text":"Simply press keys in the direction you'd\nlike to move quickly in sequence. For example,\n[color=#aaa]F-G-H[/color] will move the [b]cursor[/b] left. Think of it as\n\"rolling\" your fingers."},{"time":39.307479163689344,"duration":3.470325203252033,"type":"text","text":"Try it out!"},{"time":45.127397862876336,"duration":5.647560975609756,"type":"text","text":"Aah! Maybe I should have told you sooner.\n[color=acred]Red[/color] notes harm you. Don't let your health\ndrop to zero!"},{"time":52.26622155662475,"duration":8.159756097560976,"type":"text","text":"[color=acblue]Blue[/color] notes are [b]hold notes[/b]. You'll score as long as\nyour [b]cursor[/b] is above them while they pass. There's\nno need to tap - just be there!"},{"time":71.89623169937755,"duration":7.2804878048780495,"type":"text","text":"The last kind of notes are [color=#73faff]teal[/color] notes. Here's\nwhere [b]tapping[/b] comes into play! You must\npress a [b]tap key[/b] while the cursor is above them."},{"time":79.35605895499874,"duration":6.757113821138212,"type":"text","text":"There are lots of tap keys, but [color=#aaa]Space[/color] \nand [color=#aaa]Left Control[/color] are popular. You can\nfind more in settings. Give it a shot!"},{"time":98.9947934465497,"duration":3.722053462940462,"type":"text","text":"There are more advanced mechanics, but\nthat's all we have time for today. Have fun!"}]}